    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/FT_Merchant05/status/2036169911030939672",
      "reply_text": "Fair point. Injuries are a big factor in Embiid's decline.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-23T22:14:58.004630+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/therealBeede/status/2036198828378870269",
      "reply_text": "Timeouts like that can be game-changers. Communication with refs is key.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-23T22:15:59.310489+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NotLikeLuka/status/2036194065075560717",
      "reply_text": "Impressive numbers, but playoffs are where it really matters. His 73 points game was insane.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-23T22:16:38.217401+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BetsByCash/status/2036199084306940347",
      "reply_text": "Yeah he's playing with a fire in his belly. That's what happens when you're fighting for what matters most.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-23T22:17:35.548208+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/EnjoyBBall/status/2036194827377758664",
      "reply_text": "Not far enough. They're still figuring things out.",
