    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/ShamsCTESPN/status/2036198765195862280",
      "reply_text": "That's the one award that really matters for front office guys. The rest are all player-centric.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-23T22:19:02.456377+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BySamGordon/status/2036172615157534794",
      "reply_text": "Favorites don't always mean much without Curry. This one's gonna be a battle.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-23T22:19:53.051291+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/nosyone4/status/2036182357800104344",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, their shooting woes were on full display. Free throw shooting is crucial in the tournament",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-23T22:30:11.956161+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/FanDuel/status/2036202987018678709",
